msgid "Kurtz's Warrior"
msgstr "El guerrero de Kurtz"

msgid "Interlude II: Kurtz's Warrior"
msgstr "Interludio II: El guerrero de Kurtz"

msgid ""
"You retire to your cabin to get as much rest as possible in preparation for what awaits you tomorrow.\n"
"For a moment, you think that the combination of all the horrors you've experienced on the journey and the apprehension at facing Kurtz in his own territory is going to mean sleep eludes you.\n"
"Nevertheless, you sink into a restless sleep, as if your subconscious fitfully refuses to let your mind gradually sink into an ocean of darkness."
msgstr ""
"Te retiras a tu camarote con la intención de descansar lo máximo posible, preparándote para el día que te espera mañana.\n"
"Por un momento, te asalta el pensamiento de que todos los horrores vividos durante este viaje, junto con la creciente ansiedad de enfrentarte a Kurtz en su propio territorio, harán imposible que concilies el sueño.\n"
"Sin embargo, caes en un sueño inquieto, como si tu subconsciente se resistiera a que tu mente se pierda lentamente en un océano de tinieblas."

